DESCRIPTION:Join Merlin Rainwater\\\, creator of Seattle’s Infamous Redline
	 Guide\\\, and Tom Fucoloro\\\, Founder and Editor of the Seattle Bike Blo
	g and author of Biking Uphill in the Rain: The Story of Seattle from behin
	d the Handlebars\\\, for a bicycle tour exploring the history of Seattle b
	icycle infrastructure. \\nThis tour requires riding a bicycle between mult
	iple sites in Seattle\\\, totaling close to 10 miles and starting in the C
	entral District. Please bring your own bike. Helmets and lights will be re
	quired. For any accessibility support\\\, or general inquiries\\\, email p
